       // Generate P95/P99 routing latency
       // Context detection accuracy
       // Agent coordination success rate
     }
   }
   ```

3. **SLO Monitoring Integration**
   ```bash
   # scripts/uris-slo-monitor.ts
   # Monitor URIS SLO targets:
   # - Routing latency P95 < 50ms
   # - Context detection accuracy > 90%
   # - Consensus success rate > 95%
   ```

4. **Real-time Dashboard Data**
   - Extend current circuit breaker monitoring
   - Add URIS routing metrics
   - Performance trend analysis

